11/12/98
  Vld2 is working in mpeg2parser and mpeg2dec!
  4-bit lookup is faster than single-bit loopup by ~15% in running mpeg2parser
  on 100 frames of echo1 ES bitstream.

  Convert functions in inport and vld to inline functions to speed up.
  Results of running 100 frame of mpeg2parser
  (using the ~/Data/benchmark.mpg2 bitstream):
      Original:			31.0u 0.0s 0:46 66% 0+0k 0+0io 0pf+0w
      New Vld:			27.0u 0.0s 0:41 64% 0+0k 0+0io 0pf+0w
      Inline inport/vld:	21.0u 0.0s 0:31 66% 0+0k 0+0io 0pf+0w
      Inline util/info:		20.0u 0.0s 0:22 90% 0+0k 0+0io 0pf+0w
      -O3 compile option:	16.0u 0.0s 0:16 94% 0+0k 0+0io 0pf+0w

